Package: nginx-modsecurity-quic
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Build System <build@example.com>
Depends: libpcre3, zlib1g, libc6, libxml2, libmaxminddb0, libfuzzy2, liblua5.3-0, libyajl2, libcurl4
Recommends: systemd
Provides: nginx
Conflicts: nginx-core, nginx-full, nginx-light, nginx
Description: NGINX with ModSecurity, Brotli, HTTP/3, and more
 High-performance HTTP and reverse proxy server with:
 - ModSecurity WAF integration
 - HTTP/3 QUIC support
 - Brotli compression
 - Multiple dynamic modules
 - Jemalloc memory allocator
